    public class Main_Panel
extends javax.swing.JPanel
implements java.awt.event.ActionListener, java.beans.PropertyChangeListener
    This Class creates the GUI application and starts background threads for the data elaboration. It also provides methods to elaborates the data and display it correctly on the screen
